    "本工具基于社区共建，数据遵循 署名、非商业性使用、相同方式共享 的 CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 协议共享。" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "This tool is built by the community. Its data is shared under the CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 license (Attribution–NonCommercial–ShareAlike)."
