    },
    "汇集大量动画、漫画、游戏等作品的实地取景地标与配套截图，为你的巡礼做好准备。" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "A rich collection of real-world filming locations and matching screenshots from anime, manga, games, and more — everything you need to prepare for your pilgrimage."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "アニメ・マンガ・ゲームなど数多くの作品の実際のロケ地と対応するスクリーンショットを集約。巡礼の準備に役立ちます。"
          }
        }
      }
