    "要使用该功能，请在设备的\"设置\"中允许应用访问%@" : {
      "comment" : "Permission alert body; %@ is the resource name, e.g. Camera",
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "To use this feature, please allow this app to access %@ in Settings."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "この機能を使用するには、デバイスの「設定」でこのアプリの%@へのアクセスを許可してください。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "请在设备的\"设置\"中允许应用访问相机" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Please allow this app to access the camera in Settings."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "デバイスの「設定」でこのアプリのカメラへのアクセスを許可してください。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "身处巡礼地附近？快速查找你当前位置周围的动画取景地，开启一场说走就走的发现之旅。" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Near a pilgrimage spot? Quickly find anime filming locations around you and set off on a spur-of-the-moment journey of discovery."
          }
        },
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "聖地の近くにいますか？現在地周辺のアニメロケ地をすばやく見つけて、思い立ったらすぐに発見の旅へ。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
